description: DEMOLITION OF EXISTING BUILDINGS AND DEVELOPMENT OF A MIXED USE SCHEME COMPRISED OF 5 BUILDINGS RANGING BETWEEN 5 AND 27 STOREYS HIGH (MAXIMUM HEIGHT OF 96.5M AOD TO TOP ROOF PLANT), COMPRISING 336 RESIDENTIAL UNITS (CLASS C3), 2,502SQM OF OFFICE SPACE (CLASS B1), 1,200 OF RETAIL (CLASS A1-A4), 528SQM OF OFFICE OF RETAIL (CLASS B1 OR A1-A4) AND 154SQM OF ANCILLARY RESIDENTIAL FLOORSPACE (RESIDENTIS GYM), 79 BASEMENT CAR PARKING SPACES TOGETHER WITH ACCESS, HARD AND SOFT LANDSCAPING AND OTHER ASSOICATED WORKS INCIDENTIAL TO THE DEVELOPMENT.
